data.description: Charming and affordable ranch home in Eagle River! Convenient location in an established neighborhood. Several updates include: new carpet, laminate flooring in kitchen and bathroom, interior paint, stainless steel appliances, metal roof, plus a  240SF 1 car garage! Plenty of space for storage. You will love the level, 1/4 acre fenced yard. This home really does have it all!
